<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | Certificate Hub</title>
    <style>
        /* General Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f7f9fc, #e3f2fd);
            color: #333;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1976d2, #2196f3);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        header .logo h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
        }

        .about-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease;
        }

        .about p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease;
        }

        .about h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #2196f3;
            margin: 30px 0 15px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
        }

        .about ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .about ul li {
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: #f0f4ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .about ul li:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: #1976d2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #ffcc00;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header .logo h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            nav ul li a {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .about h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .about ul li {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>Certificate Hub</h1>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>Welcome to Certificate Hub</h2>
            <p>Your one-stop platform for seamless and efficient application for government certificates like Caste, Income, and EWS.</p>

            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>To make government services accessible, transparent, and easy for every citizen.</p>

            <h3>What We Offer</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Caste Certificate:</strong> Apply and track your caste certificate in just a few clicks.</li>
                <li><strong>Income Certificate:</strong> Submit income details for official documentation.</li>
                <li><strong>EWS Certificate:</strong> Fast and secure processing for economic support.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>User-Friendly:</strong> Intuitive interface for all users.</li>
                <li><strong>Secure:</strong> Advanced data protection and security protocols.</li>
                <li><strong>Real-Time Updates:</strong> Instant notifications for all updates.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Certificate Hub. All Rights Reserved. | <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
